                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-16/debates/6078a39c-56bb-4bd1-8c41-c93358b99d55/TradeBill(SecondSitting)"><u>Second Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 23</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-18/debates/8c0e92f5-83e2-442e-bbdc-4dfe6be1c8c2/TradeBill(ThirdSitting)"><u>Third Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 63</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-18/debates/685680ab-7a7c-43c7-aa40-1d8c3884da1a/TradeBill(FourthSitting)"><u>Fourth Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 87</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-23/debates/1ca7f399-f886-4884-9728-4e71e8452e9c/TradeBill(FifthSitting)"><u>Fifth Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 139</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-23/debates/8c7fb4ef-d875-402d-b982-d26f54ff8747/TradeBill(SixthSitting)"><u>Sixth Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 175</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-25/debates/d431ea95-d414-4b49-9a6b-885518911b1e/TradeBill(SeventhSitting)"><u>Seventh Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 247</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-06-25/debates/24f16400-76a3-4e0c-bfea-2ebe215f51c5/TradeBill(EighthSitting)"><u>Eighth Sitting Vol. 677 Col. 271</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Report and Third Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>20 July 2020</p>
